"""Verself Aspect CLI module.

Declares AXL extension dependencies. Today the durable surface uses only the
built-in @aspect extension; this file exists so `aspect axl add` can extend the
graph in the future without restructuring the workspace.

The Aspect binary version is pinned in the devtools catalog and installed by
scripts/bootstrap. This file is NOT the version-of-record for the aspect
binary.
"""
